  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Serialization_JsonSerializer'>Class JsonSerializer    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Serialization/JsonSerializer.cs#L40'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Serializes objects that implement IJsonSerializable to JSON strings.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class JsonSerializer : IJsonSerializer</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.html'>JsonSerializer</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.IJsonSerializer.html'>IJsonSerializer</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.IsComplexJsonValue(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.IsComplexJsonValue(System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Serialization_JsonSerializer_IsComplexJsonValue_System_String_'>IsComplexJsonValue(string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Serialization/JsonSerializer.cs#L107'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Determines if a string value represents a complex JSON structure (object or array).</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private static bool IsComplexJsonValue(string value)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>value</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.Serialize``1(``0)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.Serialize``1(``0)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Serialization_JsonSerializer_Serialize__1___0_'>Serialize&lt;T&gt;(T)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Serialization/JsonSerializer.cs#L50'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Serializes an object to a JSON string.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic string Serialize&lt;T&gt;(T instance) where T : IJsonSerializable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>instance</code> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The instance to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A JSON string representation of the object.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The type of the object to serialize, which must implement IJsonSerializable.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when instance is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Exceptions.JsonSerializationException.html'>JsonSerializationException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.JsonSerializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when serialization fails.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
